Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.99,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:660743,662996}Huh? Then Kozue-kun is—{NOTE:え？じゃ、こずえくんは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:06.87,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:662996,666875}Yes. She's with one of the scouts and is going to Marunichi Textiles headquarters right now.{NOTE:そうなの。丸日紡績へスカウトの人と行って。}
