Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.46,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:668668,670461}Marunichi Textiles, huh…?{NOTE:スカウトの人と丸日紡績へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:670461,672505}Why? Why are you giving up on high school?{NOTE:なぜ？なぜ進学を辞めるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.42,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:674757,676426}We're facing quite a pinch.{NOTE:今のままのは内のピンチなんだぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:18.17,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:676426,678178}All right then, see you.{NOTE:じゃ、さようなら。}
