Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.43,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:679095,680430}I didn't have to look back to know.{NOTE:X向かなくて分かっていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.68,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:680430,682682}There is no doubt she murmured it while looking at my back.{NOTE:僕の背を見て呟いていた間違いない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.80,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:682682,684809}Poor Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:可哀想。努くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.93,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:686227,687937}Kozue-kun is doing this for my sake.{NOTE:こずえくんは僕のために。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.06,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:687937,690064}If that's not it, what else could it be?!{NOTE:でなきゃそんな馬鹿なことするもんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.40,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:691441,692400}That must be it!{NOTE:そうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:33.40,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:692400,693401}Excuse me, ma'am!{NOTE:じゃ、叔母さん！}
