Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:44.16,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:702577,704162}Kozue-kun, you idiot!{NOTE:馬鹿なこずえくん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.78,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:704162,705788}Why would you do such thing?{NOTE:何でXXX？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:48.58,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:705788,708583}Why? You're better than that.{NOTE:何で？いい奴何だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.66,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:708583,709666}Just wait.{NOTE:待ってよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:52.12,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:709666,712128}I will never let you make that kind of sacrifice for me.{NOTE:絶対に君を僕の犠牲になるとさせるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.05,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:715465,718050}If she signs the contract, it's all over.{NOTE:契約書にサインをしてしまったらお終いだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:01.51,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:718050,721512}I have to make it there in time no matter what.{NOTE:それまで何が何でも丸日紡績へ行かなくては。}
