Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.27,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:775233,776276}Dammit!{NOTE:ちくしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.52,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:776276,778528}Why does it have to break when I'm almost there?{NOTE:もう少しで丸日紡績だって言うのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:12:59.44,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:778528,779445}How was it?{NOTE:どうです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.28,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:779445,781281}Do you like our volleyball club?{NOTE:気に入りましたか？我がバレー部。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:781281,782490}Yes. They're great.{NOTE:え。凄いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:782490,784409}Contracted players are truly something else.{NOTE:やっぱり実業は違うわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.28,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:784409,787287}No, no. I'm sure you'll become our company's ace in no time, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:いいえ、いいえ。鮎原さんが直ぐ我が社のエースに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.49,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:787287,789497}Mr. President will surely be delighted.{NOTE:社長もきっとお喜びになるでしょう。}
