Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:15.50,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:794377,795503}Step inside.{NOTE:入りたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.87,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:795503,796879}After you, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:さ、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:21.63,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:800925,801634}Oh?{NOTE:お。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.92,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:802051,804929}Mr. President, I brought Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:あ、社長。鮎原こずえさんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:26.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:804929,806597}Good day, Mr. President.{NOTE:よろしくお願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.60,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:807056,809600}No need to be so stiff. Please, sit down.{NOTE:え、さ、さ。どうぞ。そこにかけなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:809600,810810}Okay.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.81,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:816065,818818}I know a lot about you.{NOTE:君のことは私もよく知っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.48,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:818818,822488}To cut things short, I'd be thrilled to see you\Nuse your great talent for my company.{NOTE:なんとしても内の社で実力を発揮してもらいたい。頼みますよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:823031,824949}Thank you, Mr. President.{NOTE:はい。有難うございます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.78,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:825658,827785}Your only job will be volleyball.{NOTE:バレー一筋に打ち込んでください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:50.91,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:827785,830913}We'll arrange it so that you have enough freedom.{NOTE:仕事の方は適当に融通つけるからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:830913,833708}Oh, please don't. I don't want that.{NOTE:あら、だって。そんなの嫌だわ。}
