Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:834751,837712}I don't want to be treated specially just because I play volleyball.{NOTE:バレーをやるからって特別扱いされるのは嫌です。}
