Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.17,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:842592,845178}I guess you have a point there…{NOTE:ん、それはそうだが、んん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:845178,847972}Of course, I want to be paid for my work.{NOTE:私バレーでお給料もらうじゃありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:847972,850350}But I'd rather have a regular job like everyone else.{NOTE:仕事は仕事。バリバリやります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.80,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:850350,851809}Very well.{NOTE:ん、よろしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:15.10,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:851809,855104}Your amateur sportsman attitude is charming.{NOTE:君のアマチュアスポーツ推進が気に入ったぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:855104,856314}Thank you.{NOTE:どうも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.40,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:856314,859400}You made a really good catch,\Nfinding such a strong-willed young lady.{NOTE:が君大手柄だ。大したお嬢さんを用途としたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.81,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:859400,860818}Thank you very much, Mr. President.{NOTE:は、恐れ入ります、社長。}
