Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.00,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:875208,877001}Hahaha.{NOTE:あははは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:41.46,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:878211,881464}At any rate, Ayuhara-kun,\Nyou're still underage, aren't you?{NOTE:だが、鮎原くん、君は確か未だ未成年だったろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:882090,883424}Yes. That's correct…{NOTE:え。そうですが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:48.51,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:884842,888513}Then we'll need the consent of your parents before signing the contract.{NOTE:ん、それなら契約にはご両親のOKが必要だね。}
