Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.35,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:891682,893351}Ah, don't worry.{NOTE:や、何。心配いらん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:57.43,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:893351,897438}I'll talk to your parents personally. I'm sure I'll get them to agree.{NOTE:え、ご両親には私からよくお話してみる。きっと賛成してくださるでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:58.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:898147,898856}I hope so.{NOTE:そうですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.77,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:898856,900775}Taxi{NOTE:タクシー}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.04,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:916249,917041}Kozue?{NOTE:こずえ。}
