Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:22.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:921796,922505}Ah?{NOTE:あ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:33.30,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:930221,933307}Good day. I presume you're Ayuhara-kun's father?{NOTE:これは、これは。あなたは鮎原くんのお父さんでしたか？}
