Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.22,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:936017,937228}You came at the right moment.{NOTE:あ、丁度よかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:42.23,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:937228,942233}I wanted to talk to you regarding your daughter's contract.{NOTE:お嬢さんの契約に関してはお父様にお話しておかなければならんこともありましたので。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.69,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:942233,943693}Please, come with me to my office.{NOTE:さ、さ。どうぞ。こちらへ。}
