Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.62,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:954620,957623}I'm sure Mr. President will successfully persuade your dad.{NOTE:きっと社長は上手く君のパパを丸めてくれるよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.58,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:957623,958583}Oh, where are you going?{NOTE:あ、どこ行くんです？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:958583,960501}To see the volleyball club's practice.{NOTE:バレーの練習を見てきます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.46,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:964338,966466}First of all, I'm glad that you're here…{NOTE:え、一つ今日は私が如何に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:08.75,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:966466,968759}Mr. President, what was it\Nyou wanted to talk to me about?{NOTE:しかし社長さん、父親としましては…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.30,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:968759,970303}Please, let's not rush the subject.{NOTE:ま、いいじゃないですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:14.64,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:970303,974640}First of all, I wanted to tell you\Nthat I'm a big fan of volleyball and Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:バレーファンであり鮎原さんファンであるからについてじっくりお話しいたしますかな。}
