Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:35.32,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:993159,995328}Did I make wrong choice?{NOTE:私のしたことは間違ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.41,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:995328,997413}Is that it, Ayuhara Kozue?{NOTE:そうだったな、鮎原こずえ？}
