Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:42.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002043,1002752}Huh?{NOTE:は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.67,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003169,1004670}Throw us the ball!{NOTE:ボールを投げて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006255,1007964}No. I didn't go wrong.{NOTE:いいえ。間違ってやしない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.30,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012845,1014305}Wow, wonderful serve.{NOTE:あ。凄いサーブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.68,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015223,1017683}It curved mid-air and fell perpendicularly.{NOTE:その変まで来て、垂直の落ちたのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:01.14,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018059,1021145}I had a hunch that I knew her face from somewhere.{NOTE:通りてどこかで見た顔だと思ったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.60,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021521,1023606}Oh, Captain, you know her?{NOTE:あや、キャプテンあの人知ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.65,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024440,1025650}Ayuhara Kozue.{NOTE:鮎原こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.77,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025650,1027777}She's the junior Japan's volleyball representative.{NOTE:ジュニアバレーの日本代表よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.65,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027777,1030655}So she's the captain of\NFujimi Middle School's volleyball club?{NOTE:じゃ、富士見中学バレー部のキャプテンね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.48,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030655,1031489}Whoa.{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.61,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031489,1033616}So that serve must have been the "falling leaf".{NOTE:今のサーブは「木の葉落とし」だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:16.24,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033616,1036244}I thought she was going to high school, though?{NOTE:進学するって聞いてたけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.91,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036244,1037912}Maybe she's here to join our club?{NOTE:内に入ることになったのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.45,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038412,1039455}Let's try calling her.{NOTE:呼んでみましょうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.62,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039455,1040623}Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040623,1041332}Yes?{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.87,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041332,1043876}You're Ayuhara Kozue from Fujimi Middle School, right?{NOTE:あなた富士見中の鮎原こずえでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043876,1045002}I am. Nice to meet you.{NOTE:はい。よろしく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.37,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046169,1047379}I knew it!{NOTE:やっぱり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:28.83,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047379,1048839}You're joining our club, aren't you?{NOTE:私達の仲間に成るのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049715,1050299}I am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:34.38,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051342,1054387}Your daughter has made her decision very carefully. It's not on a whim.{NOTE:お嬢さんの決心は1時の浮ついた気持ちじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:39.64,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054387,1059642}She'd like to test her skills at our prestigious Marunichi Textiles' volleyball club.{NOTE:バレーボール界の名門我が丸日紡績で力いっぱい自分の実力を試してみたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.01,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059642,1061018}And she wants to work, too.{NOTE:そして仕事もしたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.47,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061018,1062478}Her resolve is incredible.{NOTE:純粋な気持ちです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:45.18,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062478,1065189}What do you think of it as her father?{NOTE:お父さん。どうでしょう？ここは一つ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.02,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1065189,1066023}Hmm…{NOTE:は～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:50.40,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066023,1070403}But what's her motivation for all of this?{NOTE:しかし娘の本当の考えがどこにあるのか？一体。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.90,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070403,1071904}That matter is quite clear to me.{NOTE:それならはっきりしてるでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:55.90,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071904,1075908}Your daughter just wants to play volleyball to her heart's content, don't you think?{NOTE:悪が丸日で思う存分戦いたい。こういうことではないのですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:56.74,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075908,1076742}I see…{NOTE:は～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.37,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085001,1086377}Amazing!{NOTE:素晴らしいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.37,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085626,1086377}So cool!{NOTE:かっこいい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.33,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086377,1087336}Kozue-kun!{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087336,1088754}Tsutomu-kun, what are you doing here?{NOTE:努くん。どうして？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:12.46,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090923,1092466}Who is he?{NOTE:何なの彼？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:14.01,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092466,1094010}He must be her boyfriend.{NOTE:彼女のボーイフレンド、きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.34,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094927,1097346}That's my line. What did you come here for?{NOTE:君はあそこで何をしていた？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.22,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097346,1099223}What are you doing at this company?{NOTE:この会社は君の何なんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099223,1100433}What am I doing, you ask…{NOTE:何いって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:23.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100433,1103144}I'm going to get a job here once I graduate from middle school.{NOTE:学校卒業したら私ここへ就職するの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:23.93,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103144,1103936}Idiot!{NOTE:馬鹿！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.43,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103936,1104437}Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.60,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104437,1105605}What a scumbag!{NOTE:酷いわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.39,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105605,1108399}Who'd hit a girl? Let's stop him!{NOTE:暴力不良何て…止めしてましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.56,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108399,1109567}Stop.{NOTE:お止しなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:30.81,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109567,1110818}We're in the middle of practice.{NOTE:練習中よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.57,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110818,1112570}Think only about volleyball during practice.{NOTE:練習中はバレーのことだけ考えて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.32,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113154,1115322}People are watching,\Nso let's talk somewhere in private.{NOTE:人はいるから。向こうで話そう。さ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119744,1121162}What are you doing?{NOTE:ん、何よするの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121162,1125249}Slapping and pulling me out of the blue?\NTsutomu-kun, you're way out of your bounds!{NOTE:いきなり突き飛ばしたり張ってきたり、いくら努くんだって許せないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.42,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126207,1129420}If I don't do this, you won't open your eyes.{NOTE:こうでもしなきゃ。君の目が覚めないと思ったからだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129420,1130755}What I do is none of your business.{NOTE:大きなお世話よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:53.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130755,1133966}I live my life how I want to, so don't you get in my way.{NOTE:私は私の考えでやってるんだから、邪魔しないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.42,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133966,1135426}You're such a liar!{NOTE:嘘つき！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.42,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135426,1138429}You told me you wanted to go to high school and play volleyball there.{NOTE:君は高校へ進んで、バレーをやるって言ったはずだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:00.30,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138429,1140306}Where did that passion go?{NOTE:その情熱は？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140306,1142558}I changed my mind.{NOTE:だから、それは気が変わったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142558,1143726}Changed your mind?{NOTE:変わった？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:05.56,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143726,1145561}I know exactly what made you do it.{NOTE:変わった理由は分かっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:11.35,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145561,1151359}You're going to use your contract money to let me go to high school. Am I right?!{NOTE:君は僕にもらった契約金を私に高校へ進学しろうっていうつもりだ。そうだろう？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:11.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151359,1151942}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:17.57,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153527,1157573}Are you really trying to push your self-important compassion down my throat, Kozue-kun?{NOTE:そんなこずえくんの独り善がりの同情を僕に押し付けるつもりか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157573,1159200}That's a terrible thing to say!{NOTE:酷い。酷いわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159200,1160784}"Push down your throat"?!{NOTE:押し付けるなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.95,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160784,1162953}I'm sorry, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:すまない、こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.37,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162953,1165373}I just don't want that kind of sympathy.{NOTE:しかし、そんな同情はごめんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.25,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166331,1168250}Now that's problematic…{NOTE:困りましたな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.17,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171962,1173172}I'll make myself clear.{NOTE:はっきり言うよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.59,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173172,1174590}I don't want that money.{NOTE:僕はそんな金など欲しくない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.21,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175257,1176217}Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:40.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176967,1180721}How am I supposed to go to high school when I know that you sacrificed yourself for it?{NOTE:君を犠牲にして僕だけしといてノコノコ進学できるもんか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:42.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181847,1182848}Sacrificed?{NOTE:犠牲？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182848,1184392}Don't be absurd.{NOTE:大げさなこと言わないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184392,1186602}If I work here, I can play volleyball all I want.{NOTE:ここへ入ったってバレーがちゃんとできるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.77,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186602,1187770}Then what about the school?{NOTE:じゃ、学校はどうする？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:49.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188437,1189814}I don't care about it anymore.{NOTE:そ、そんなどうだっていいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.85,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189814,1190856}What?!{NOTE:何？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.02,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190856,1192024}Cut it out already!{NOTE:いい加減にしろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:52.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192024,1192524}Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.11,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193359,1195110}They've been gone a long time…{NOTE:未だ戻ってこないわ、あの二人。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.73,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195110,1196737}He's quite the delinquent, don't you think?{NOTE:あいつ不良だったんじゃない?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.61,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196737,1197613}Hey.{NOTE:ちょっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.36,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197613,1199365}How long are you going to think about her?{NOTE:いつまで気にしてるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.49,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199365,1200491}Sorry.{NOTE:すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.86,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200491,1202868}But it's only natural to think about her.{NOTE:けど、気になるのは当たり前です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.28,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202868,1205287}We'll become even stronger with her around.{NOTE:あの子は来てくれたら凄い戦力になるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.62,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205287,1206622}No, we won't.{NOTE:成らないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:07.24,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1206622,1207248}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.20,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207248,1208207}What makes you say that?{NOTE:なぜですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.96,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208207,1210960}She has as much talent as you, no more and no less.{NOTE:少なくとも今の様子ではあなた達と同じよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:16.09,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212128,1216090}When she entered our court,\Nher thoughts were somewhere else.{NOTE:あの子はバレーコートの中に行って、バレー意外のこと考えていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.13,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216090,1218134}Her technique was good but her soul was missing.{NOTE:だからテクニックだけで魂が死んでたよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:22.63,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221804,1222638}Kozue-kun.{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.22,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222638,1224223}You were wrong.{NOTE:君は間違っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:28.56,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224223,1228561}You won't earn points with people\Nwith this kind of such selfish, pushy behavior.{NOTE:そんな自分勝手ななプレイをしちゃってポイントを稼ぐことはできないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.43,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228561,1230438}But I couldn't just stand there doing nothing.{NOTE:だって、見ていられなかったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230438,1232857}You always took the school seriously, Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:あんなに勉強熱心だった努くんが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.77,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233858,1236777}Come on, don't pity me.{NOTE:おいおい、僕を舐めないでくれよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:39.82,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236777,1239822}Do you really think feeling sorry for me will have made me happy?{NOTE:女の子に同情されて喜ぶとでも思ってたのかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.65,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241698,1242658}Shocking, isn't it?{NOTE:ショックだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.45,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243658,1245453}I don't need anyone's help.{NOTE:僕はお恵みがいらないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:46.45,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245453,1246454}Not a single yen.{NOTE:一円だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246454,1247288}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:50.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249290,1250499}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.49,0:20:53.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250499,1253461}I knew you'd shout at me, Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:きっと努くんに叱られると思ってた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:56.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253461,1256464}And yet, I still wanted to do something for you.{NOTE:それでもやっぱりXXしてられなかったの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:58.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256464,1258966}Even if it you didn't want anything.{NOTE:例え無駄でもやってみようと思ったのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.63,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258966,1260634}I understand.{NOTE:分かってるさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.09,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260634,1262094}I understand it very well.{NOTE:よく分かってるんだそんなことは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.51,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263304,1264513}Thank you, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:有難う、こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.56,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269101,1270561}Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.48,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273898,1276484}Okay then, let's proceed with the contract.{NOTE:じゃ、契約書の方どうかお願いします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.69,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276984,1278694}Wait a moment.{NOTE:君ちょっと待ちたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:22.07,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278694,1282072}I gave up on getting her to come to my team.{NOTE:私は諦めたよ。彼女にうちのチームに来てもらうとは。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.03,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282072,1283032}Eh?{NOTE:え？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.28,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283032,1285284}I am truly sorry for it, but it can't be helped.{NOTE:誠に残念だがやもう得ん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.95,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285284,1287953}She's truly a great girl.{NOTE:いいお嬢さんだ。実に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:36.25,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287953,1296253}I decided to withdraw the contract\Nand ask again three years from now on.{NOTE:私は三年後のチャンスに改めてお願いすることとして今回を潔く契約を撤回することにしたよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.25,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296253,1298255}{\fad(0,1500)}Eh…{NOTE:え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:44.26,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301842,1304261}That's how things are, Ayuhara-kun.{NOTE:そういうわけだから、鮎原くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:49.30,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304720,1309308}So please proceed as you initially planned\Nand play in a high school club.{NOTE:で、最初の考え通り進学して高校バレーで活躍してください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:54.81,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1311894,1314814}It's regrettable. I hope we meet again some day.{NOTE:残念が、又いつか会うこともあるでしょ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314814,1316607}I'm sorry, Mr. President.{NOTE:社長さん、すみません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.65,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317441,1319652}Oh, no, you really don't need to apologize to me.{NOTE:ん、誤ることはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:05.49,Default,President,1,1,0,,{TIME:1319652,1325491}But be careful. If you're still free three years from now,\NI will personally go scouting to your house.{NOTE:それより、三年後ご用事。下手をすると私自身があんたの家へスカウトに行きますぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:09.11,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325491,1329119}Ah… If I actually do that,\Nthat boy might lose his means of livelihood…{NOTE:いいや、そんなことしたら、彼が飯の食い上げになるか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:11.41,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1329119,1331413}– Hahaha.\N– Mr. President…{NOTE:—はははは。\\N—社長。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:14.83,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332414,1334834}Mr. President knows everything.{NOTE:社長さんは何もかも知っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.52,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354728,1356522}Oh, it's Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:あら、鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.06,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356522,1358065}She's with the boy from before.{NOTE:さっきの子も一緒だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:40.02,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358732,1360025}They've patched things up?{NOTE:仲直りしたのかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:43.57,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360943,1363571}To you, who for a single day were my team mates…{NOTE:今日一日のチームメートだった皆さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.57,0:22:44.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363571,1364362}Goodbye!{NOTE:さようなら！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:47.65,Alternative,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366615,1367658}"Falling leaf" again.{NOTE:「木の葉落とし」ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.65,0:22:49.49,Alternative,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1367658,1369493}A one-trick pony!{NOTE:一度見れば…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.74,0:22:51.28,Alternative,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1370744,1371287}Ah!?{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:54.83,Default,Player,0,0,0,,{TIME:1373747,1374832}Her soul… is right here.{NOTE:魂が生きていたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:02.67,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380838,1382673}Let's go home.{NOTE:さ、帰ろうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:07.21,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385426,1387219}That was "falling leaf", huh…?{NOTE:あれが「木の葉落とし」じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:08.05,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1387219,1388053}What a pity.{NOTE:惜しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:09.17,Default,Head hunter,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388053,1389179}What a real pity…{NOTE:惜しいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:13.51,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1391264,1393517}Well then, I'm in a hurry.{NOTE:それじゃ、僕ちょっと急ぎますから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.51,0:23:14.76,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1393517,1394768}I see.{NOTE:そうかね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:16.68,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394768,1396687}Sorry for making you worry.{NOTE:どうも心配をかけてすすまなかったね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:19.10,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1396687,1399106}No worries. Well, see you.{NOTE:いいえ。じゃ、失礼します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:23.23,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399815,1403235}Tsutomu-kun and you seem to be walking different paths now.{NOTE:どうやら努くんとお前とは別々の道を歩くらしいな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:25.48,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1403235,1405487}But, each person has their own way.{NOTE:人にはそれぞれの道がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:27.23,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1405487,1407239}Today, you learned something important.{NOTE:大事なこと勉強したよだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.65,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407239,1408657}Would you like to come back by taxi?{NOTE:タクシーで帰るかね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:32.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408657,1412119}I want to walk with you for a bit longer, Papa.{NOTE:んん、私も少しパパと一緒に歩いてみたいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:33.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412119,1413370}Can we?{NOTE:いいでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:35.24,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414038,1415246}Hm? Heh.{NOTE:ん？へへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:36.37,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:1415246,1416373}Of course.{NOTE:発想はいいだろうな。}
